USERS-
1.	Ride taker-
Student who requests a ride from pickup location to destination
2.	Ride giver-
Student who offers a ride with his/her own car to a particular destination at a specified time

Product Backlog-
STORY001-
As a ride taker, I want to book a ride from pickup location to drop off location so that I can reach the destination
STORY002-
As a ride giver , I want to post my ride availability so that I can offer rides to other students
STORY003-
As a ride taker, I want to verify if the ride giver is a student so that I can have a safe drive
STORY004-
As a ride giver, I want to collect money from giving rides so that I can help students as well as earn money
STORY005-
As a ride taker, I want to pay an amount of money lesser than taxi companies for the ride taken so that I do not spend a lot of money for travel
STORY006-
As a ride giver, I must be able to login with my username and password so that I have a safe entry into the application
STORY007-
As a ride taker, I must be able to login with my username and password so that I have a safe entry into the application
STORY008-
As a ride giver, I must be able to sign up with my details so that I can register into the application
STORY009-
As a ride taker, I must be able to sign up with my details so that I can register into the application
STORY010-
As a ride taker, I must be able to search for rides to my destination without logging in so that I can see if rides are available
STORY011-
As a ride taker, I must be able to book a ride only after logging in so that I can reach my slot is booked with the ride giver
STORY012-
As a ride giver, I must be able to update my personal information so that any changes in my profile are updated
STORY013-
As a ride taker, I must be able to update my personal information so that any changes in my profile are updated
STORY014-
As a ride giver, I must be able to upload pictures of my car so that the ride takers can see it
STORY015-
As a ride taker, I must be able to give rating to the ride givers after taking their ride so that I can share my ride experience


